Koffers is the automatic dependency resolution and installation tool, responsible for pulling library dependencies from repositories.

Usage:

Find a package to install:

	koffers search <pattern>

Install a package, optionally specifying a version:

	koffers install <package> [<version>]

Uninstall a package:
	koffers remove <package> [<version>]

List dependencies for a given package:
	koffers depends <package> [<version>]

List installed packages:
	koffers list